456
00:31:23,549 --> 00:31:25,231
Você...

457
00:31:27,991 --> 00:31:29,783
Holland.

458
00:31:30,662 --> 00:31:33,299
Olha, vou voltar amanhã,
certo?

459
00:31:33,300 --> 00:31:35,410
E vou trazer o Woodrue.

460
00:31:35,411 --> 00:31:38,369
Se quiser encontrar-nos,
tem uma...

